{"tid":2106110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳鴻海斥78億印度設廠製iPhone","createTime":"2020-07-13T06:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T07:05:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31cf2d2eef6714757b8cb1d678ad3a8197954dba","tid":2106110,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200712/X3UWWDM2JIKYSOPM4VAKNQQZ4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200712%2FX3UWWDM2JIKYSOPM4VAKNQQZ4Q%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=c9494fe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200712%2FX3UWWDM2JIKYSOPM4VAKNQQZ4Q%2F&h=df54158e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200712/X3UWWDM2JIKYSOPM4VAKNQQZ4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n傳鴻海斥78億印度設廠製iPhone<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q8SpBPkl1uuYmPuBj1AUDGsx8gU=/640x320/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PL6I5JXEVTZDBL72ZEZSDPSYYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq8SpBPkl1uuYmPuBj1AUDGsx8gU%3D%2F640x320%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPL6I5JXEVTZDBL72ZEZSDPSYYY.jpg&h=4336742d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果被指正尋求把iPhone生產線遷出中國，不希望供應鏈集中在同一國家。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】路透引述兩名消息人士稱，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n把部份iPhone生產線撤離中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果促生產線撤華<br />\n<br />\n路透前日報道，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n不希望iPhone供應鏈集中在同一國家。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n蘋果公司和鴻海集團均沒回應報道。<br />\n<br />\nCounterpoint科技市場研究總監Neil Shah分析指，印度勞工成本較中國便宜，於印度組裝iPhone，可減輕產品進口稅負擔，有助蘋果公司提升iPhone價格；6月亦有報道指，蘋果計劃把iPhone SE生產線從內地轉移到印度。主要經濟體正進行去中國化，華府正促使美企業把供應鏈遷出中國，甚至搬回美國；白宮經濟顧問庫德洛4月曾表示，華府將為美企承擔相關費用。日本政府也鼓勵日本企業把廠房及供應鏈搬回國內，並特設2,200億日圓援助貸款。"},{"pid":"a706